<br>
Gorangas at tree south of DP zone:<br>
with fear, 3 folks 50-55, one is cleric who will die of boredom most of the time, but that one goranga per hour that cannot be snared or feared will make up for it. May as well have the cleric loot that GSC and practice 1hb when full-mana.<br>
without fear, full group of 45-55s. Soloable, barely at 60 (I've seen it done, but they need a rez about every 60-90 min).<br>
<br>
cotieries:<br>
full group 50-55s, can get by with some lower.<br>
<br>
2-arms and 4-arms:<br>
full group, needs to be able to handle the coteries easily. <p><a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=64195'>Combat Profile</a><br>
