<br>
We were in Umbral untill a bigger guild came and pushed us out because they wanted our spot to pull Rumblecrush to.  So we decided to kill stuff on just the other side of the zone.  First pull brings all three of the mobs at the entrance... two cloaked dudes and one 4 armer.  Another cloak dude came later too.  We managed to finish them all off, since we had two groups of 50-55 which included a couple of clerics and two wizards.  The belt was on the 4 armer.  The fellas and laides were nice enough to let me have it.  So lucky maybe, or maybe they are more common there. <p><b>Jonze</b> 57 Paladin
